== TitanChat Supports

TitanChat Supports, the TitanChat addons for plugin supports

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Features

* Easy to write

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Functions

* Supporting other plugins

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Supports

=== CraftIRC2Support

* Supports relaying with CraftIRC 2

=== CraftIRC3Support

* Supports relaying with CraftIRC 3

==== FactionsSupport

* Supports Faction Tag in chat
* Use %faction in format to be replaced with your Faction Tag

=== GlobalChannel

* Globally broadcasts messages to all

=== HeroesSupport

* Supports HeroClass, ProfClass, Level and Health in chat
* Use %heroclass in format to be replaced with your HeroClass
* Use %profclass in format to be replaced with your ProfClass
* Use %level in format to be replaced with your level
* Use %health in format to be replaced with your health

=== LocalChannel

* Sends messages to players within range

=== MonsterIRCSupport

* Supports relaying with MonsterIRC

=== SimpleClansSupport

* Supports Clan Tag in chat
* Use %clan in format to be replaced with your Clan Tag

=== TitanChatFilter

* Filter function of the original built in filter
* Filter words and phrases listed in the config

=== TitanChatWorld

* Supports World Name
* Use %world in format to be replaced with the world you're in
* Uses Multiverse's World Name if Multiverse is present

=== TownySupport

* Supports Town Name, Nation Name and Title
* Use %town in format to be replaced with your town
* Use %nation in format to be replaced with your nation
* Use %title in format to be replaced with your title

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Dependecies

* TitanChat
* Whatever plugin that you are supporting

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== How to install

* Place in supports folder in TitanChat folder
* Done!

